---
title: Honey Sriracha Chicken with Roasted Sesame Carrots & Cilantro Lime Rice
description: Another work day, another dinner daydream. You know what we mean. You’re sitting at your desk and 2:00 p.m. rolls around. Suddenly, all you can think is, “Dinner...what the heck am I going to eat for dinner?!” Well, we’ve got you covered, and FYI, the answer to that question is pretty glorious. We’re talking succulent pork filet, roasted sesame carrots, and fluffy cilantro lime rice. To finish things off, the pork is drizzled in a lick-the-plate-worthy sauce made with sesame oil, scallions, ginger, honey, and sriracha. Talk about a dream come true!
